is controlled by the content of the LICENSE.GLIMMER file.

Some modifications have been made to the original Glimmer3 files.
As per the conditions of the above Glimmer3 license, all such
modifications are placed into the Public Domain. The scope of 
modifications is described in the header of each corresponding
source file. The resulting executables no longer behave like
the standard Glimmer3 executables. Thus, they have been renamed
to avoide possible confusion. See README file for more details.

